{"tid":2195880,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人仲需要買口罩？","createTime":"2020-09-09T12:30:32.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-09T17:43:24.000Z","uid":128751,"like":3,"dislike":19,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"d051897c5ca075f99ac8ab009eed10d10600c2d3","tid":2195880,"uid":128751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T12:30:32.000Z","msg":"是咁的<br />\n近期岩岩揾到一份工係做口罩批發<br />\n但係我一張單都出唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n明白好多地方口罩都好充足 <br />\n我公司因為全香港製所以都唔算賣得平<br />\n但都想係度問下有無人想買口罩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n普通口罩一箱40盒 有獨立包裝嘅一箱20盒<br />\n仲有唔同顏色嘅口罩同有花玟<br />\n全部都過哂SGS STC Lv2 岩岩過左Lv3<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有興趣嘅巴打絲打email話我知<br />\nAnnaleung000@gmail.com<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"x-large\">我真係唔想無工返啊</span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"640f9fafcd52c9de95a119f8126d293d6ac54b06","tid":2195880,"uid":335538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T12:32:51.000Z","msg":"0.5$ 一個同你收<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d93d2a01b8e2221f10abb2863d161b678095edc","tid":2195880,"uid":35671,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T12:33:02.000Z","msg":"圖？<br />\n錢？"},{"pid":"4e1021b03a48cf52e0f6ae3835313daabcd538c7","tid":2195880,"uid":2660,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T12:33:22.000